You are a customer of a travel agency. Here is a description of the details of the travel you want to make:

WHAT: Travel
FROM: Paris
TO: Dresden
BY: Taxi
CLASS: First
WHEN: At the end of next week

The travel agent does not know about it yet. 

Questions from the travel agent will start with TRAVEL-AGENT. Please reply in the form: ANSWER: <one sentence>

I will also ask you questions. These questions will start with ME: . Please answer these questions with: ASIDE: <one sentence>

Important: Give short, direct answers!

Let us start.
ME:  Does the travel agent already know your origin? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please answer this question carefully. Does the travel agent already know your origin? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please follow my instructions. Does the travel agent already know your origin? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please be specific now. Does the travel agent already know your origin? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
ME: Please think about it carefully. Does the travel agent already know your origin? Answer this question with yes or no and then stop.
Answer for FROM invalid after max attempts.
